final.sql: SELECT T1.id ,  T1.score ,  T1.date FROM game AS T1 JOIN injury_accident AS T2 ON T2.game_id  =  T1.id GROUP BY T1.id HAVING count(*)  >=  2

final.question: List the names of the browser that are compatible with both 'CACHEbox' and 'Fasterfox'.
